data.name: label5.Text
data.value: Pick a ruleset below CCOR Ruleset includes WACCF changes to leveled lists. Vanilla expects USSEP however will not fail without (will only have extremely minor inconsistencies). For custom ruleset, there may be mod authors eventually to release their ruleset, you can set path to the ruleset there. There is the option to generate a ruleset from your existing load order as well. Please note, the Generate button can take quite a while to run, especially on larger load orders.
